# Model config: Qwen3-Coder-Next (Q4_1, sharded GGUF) -- model-intrinsic only.
#
# 80B MoE, ~3B active (512 experts, 10 used). Q4_1 weights total ~47.3 GiB across
# three shards; point -m at the FIRST shard and llama.cpp loads the rest.
#
# This file holds ONLY what is intrinsic to the model (weight path + sampling).
# Card-fit tuning (context, ubatch, KV quant, split) is GPU-specific and lives in
# profiles/<machine>/qwen3-coder-next-q4.env -- e.g. profiles/r9700-dual/... targets
# the model's native 256K context with all weights in VRAM across both cards.
#
#   - Qwen3-Coder sampling: temp 0.7, top-p 0.8, top-k 20, repeat-penalty 1.05.

: "${MODEL:=Qwen3-Coder-Next/Q4_1/Qwen3-Coder-Next-Q4_1-00001-of-00003.gguf}"

LLAMA_ARGS+=(--temp 0.7 --top-p 0.8 --top-k 20 --repeat-penalty 1.05)
